casebody.data:
No. 20.

October Term, 1911.

Sidney Henry et al. v. A. B. Dick Company. Submitted May 21, 1917. Decided June 11, 1917. Mr. Hans von Briesén and Mr. Arthur von Briesen for Margaret Henry, petitioner.

Motion for leave to file bill of review in the District Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York granted.
